    <descript>
      <abstract>The dataset contains lines that designate fences, walls and other miscellaneous structures. </abstract>
      <purpose>The purpose of this dataset is to graphically represent the geographical location of land structures located as defined in the abstract within Prince William County. These structures can be walls, fences and other small miscellaneous features that are not classified as cultural features.</purpose>
